comment: Brewer (HOU) establishes a legal guarding position prior to contact by Allen (MEM)
Lee (MEM) bumps Harden (HOU), affecting his RSBQ.
Harden (HOU) does not extend his arm on the step back move against Lee (MEM)
Brewer (HOU) gets his hands on the ball while trying to take it away from Gasol (MEM).
Brewer (HOU) makes contact with the body of Lee (MEM) and the contact affects his RSBQ.
Jones (HOU) uses a pump fake to get the defending Lee (MEM) in the air. Lee 's left leg hits the back of Jones as he attempts to gather the ball for the layup.
Gasol (MEM) cleanly strips the ball from Jones (HOU), who gets the ball back.
Gasol (MEM) does not release his shot before the 24-Second clock expires. Houston gains possession on the rebound.
Randolph (MEM) makes contact across Harden's (HOU) arm/wrist, causing him to lose the ball on the drive to the basket.
